== Guides & Documentation

Key resources to support mentors, podlings, and the Incubator PMC. These guides cover onboarding, mentoring practices, governance, reporting, and lessons learned.

=== Getting Started / Orientation
- link:https://cwiki.apache.org/confluence/display/INCUBATOR/Incubator+Mentor+Quick+Start+Guide[Mentor Quick Start Guide] — fast orientation for new mentors  
- link:https://cwiki.apache.org/confluence/display/INCUBATOR/Mentor+Onboarding[Mentor Onboarding] — step-by-step entry into mentoring  
- link:https://cwiki.apache.org/confluence/display/INCUBATOR/Incubator+PMC+Onboarding[Incubator PMC Onboarding] — orientation for joining the IPMC  
- link:https://cwiki.apache.org/confluence/display/INCUBATOR/Podling+Committer+Onboarding[Podling Committer Onboarding] — what new committers need to know  
- link:https://cwiki.apache.org/confluence/display/INCUBATOR/Podling+PPMC+Onboarding[Podling PPMC Onboarding] — duties and decision-making within the PPMC  
- link:https://cwiki.apache.org/confluence/display/INCUBATOR/Podling+Orientation+Guide[Podling Orientation Guide] — introduction to incubation and ASF culture  

=== Communication and Collaboration
- link:https://cwiki.apache.org/confluence/display/INCUBATOR/Communication+in+Apache+Projects[Communication in Apache Projects] — why mailing lists matter, acceptable chat use, and meeting best practices  

=== Governance and Project Health
- link:https://cwiki.apache.org/confluence/display/INCUBATOR/Governance+in+Practice[Governance in Practice] — applying the Apache Way in daily decisions  
- link:https://cwiki.apache.org/confluence/display/INCUBATOR/Voting+and+Consensus+in+Practice[Voting and Consensus in Practice] — understanding consensus, voting types, and how decisions are made  
- link:https://cwiki.apache.org/confluence/display/INCUBATOR/Selecting+a+PMC+Chair[Selecting a PMC Chair] — how to identify and elect project leadership  
- link:https://cwiki.apache.org/confluence/display/INCUBATOR/Third-Party+Branding+Incubating+Projects[Third-Party Branding and Incubating Projects] — guidance on names, logos, and vendor neutrality  
- link:https://cwiki.apache.org/confluence/display/INCUBATOR/Legal+Basics[Legal Basics] — essential ASF legal and licensing principles for podlings  
- link:https://cwiki.apache.org/confluence/display/INCUBATOR/Interacting+with+ASF+Infrastructure[Interacting with ASF Infrastructure] — how projects work effectively with ASF Infra and shared services  
- link:https://cwiki.apache.org/confluence/display/INCUBATOR/Graduation+Criteria[Graduation Criteria] — what’s required for a podling to graduate  
- link:https://cwiki.apache.org/confluence/display/INCUBATOR/Graduation+and+Beyond[Graduation and Beyond] — the post-graduation transition process  
- link:https://cwiki.apache.org/confluence/display/INCUBATOR/Retiring+Podlings[Retiring Podlings] — how and when to retire an inactive podling  

=== Mentoring, Reporting, and Practice
- link:https://cwiki.apache.org/confluence/display/INCUBATOR/Common+Red+Flags[Common Red Flags] — issues mentors should watch for  
- link:https://cwiki.apache.org/confluence/display/INCUBATOR/Best+Practices+for+Mentors[Best Practices for Mentors] — examples and scenarios for effective mentoring  
- link:https://cwiki.apache.org/confluence/display/INCUBATOR/Mentors+Tough+Conversation+Guide[Mentors’ Tough Conversation Guide] — how to navigate difficult discussions  
- link:https://cwiki.apache.org/confluence/display/INCUBATOR/Mentor+Offboarding[Mentor Offboarding] — how mentors transition after graduation  
- link:https://cwiki.apache.org/confluence/display/TRAINING/ASF+Project+Reporting+Guidance[Project Report Guide] — preparing and submitting ASF project reports  
- link:https://cwiki.apache.org/confluence/display/INCUBATOR/How+To+Use+the+ASF+Maturity+Model[How To Use the ASF Maturity Model] — optional tool to assess community readiness  
- link:https://cwiki.apache.org/confluence/display/INCUBATOR/Vendor+Neutrality[Vendor Neutrality] — maintaining balanced, independent governance  
- link:https://cwiki.apache.org/confluence/display/INCUBATOR/International+and+Cultural+Awareness[International & Cultural Awareness] — working across languages and time zones  
